            <title>索尼 PS5《007 初露锋芒》限定版 DualSense 手柄控制器发售，639 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/956/204.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/956/204.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Wed, 27 May 2026 13:24:59 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
